Name: Forensic Factor
Title: Forensics on Trial
Desc: With four suspects, CSIs turns to the brand-new science of DNA to catch the killer.
LongDescription: In fall 1991, Toronto was paralyzed by the story of a missing six-year-old girl found raped and murdered in the boiler room of her apartment building; with four suspects, CSIs turned to the brand-new science of DNA to catch the killer.
